<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Bus Out of Service - Austria Express</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      padding: 20px 30px;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #004d26;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }

    .content p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #333333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    table th,
    table td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    table th {
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #004d26;
      display: inline-block;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999999;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      Bus Out of Service Notification - Austria Express
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <strong><%= first_name %> <%= last_name %></strong>,</p>

      <p>We regret to inform you that your scheduled bus service on <strong><%= travel_date %></strong> has been   <strong>canceled</strong> due to an unforeseen technical issue affecting the line 
        (<strong>Line Name: <%= route_name %></strong>).</p>

      <p>We sincerely apologize for the inconvenience caused. Your safety and comfort remain our top priority. We understand this may disrupt your travel plans and we’re here to help.</p>

      <p>You may choose to <strong>reschedule your trip</strong> or request a <strong>full refund</strong> through your account dashboard or by contacting our support team.</p>

      <p>If you need any assistance, please don’t hesitate to reach out.</p>

      <!-- Passenger Information -->
      <div class="section-title">Passenger Information</div>
      <table>
        <tr>
          <th>First Name</th>
          <th>Last Name</th>
          <th>Email</th>
          <th>Phone</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><%= first_name %></td>
          <td><%= last_name %></td>
          <td><a href="mailto:<%= email %>"><%= email %></a></td>
          <td><%= phone %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <!-- Booking Details -->
      <div class="section-title">Booking Details</div>
      <table>
        <tr>
          <th>Departure</th>
          <th>Route</th>
          <th>Line</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <%= departure_time %> - <%= arrival_time %>
          </td>
          <td><%= from_city %> to <%= to_city %></td>
          <td><%= route_name %></td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <th>Payment Method</th>
          <th>Total Amount</th>
          <th>Booking Number</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><%= payment_method %></td>
          <td><%= total %></td>
          <td><%= bookingNumber %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; Austria Express. All rights reserved.<br />
      This is an automated message — please do not reply directly to this email.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>